<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE DAY THOU GAVEST, LORD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na ni nei piek hi ahung beitai,
 Na thu'n khuo a thim hi Lalpa;
 Ho hi'n ka ihmut hih thieng inla,
 Thawh tiengleh chawihat na ngai hi.

[V2]
 2. Na Sapchuomte a hak a um zing,
 Lei vakna lama umte chu;
 Tichun ven loh tik umlo hielin,
 Sun leh zan in Na min gen zing.

[V3]
 3. Lei leh tuikuol a kizawm zel in,
 Khawvak thak hin vak a pui zing;
 Paucham hailo-in a zui zing hi,
 Pahchak la gi ahai ngei puoi.

[V4]
 4. Nitum ihmut phat ei hilh pen hi'n,
 Nuoilam a suohpihte a phawng;
 Chun tui kinawk banga Aw haw chuh,
 Chawllo in Van lamah chieh to.

[V5]
 5. Ahi ngut ie, Lalpa, Na gam hi,
 Lei gam banga bei ding ei puoi;
 Na Lalgam hung deta lien zel ding,
 Thu, micheng kiengah thang suok hen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>207</hymn_number>
</song>